snippet.title: Rainbow Six X Breakpoint! Ghost Recon Breakpoint Operation Amber Sky on Google Stadia!
snippet.description:
Enjoy the video? Subscribe for more and follow me on Twitch to see me live!
https://www.twitch.tv/grandnoodlelite

Get an extra month of Stadia Pro when you sign up with my referral link:
https://stadia.com/link/referrals?si_rid=13571158019252207904&si_rt=1

GrandNoodleLite's Gaming Scrapbook is a series of clips taken from games I played when I wasn't streaming. Think of these as "Stream Highlights" without the live stream.

GrandNoodleLite's Gaming Scrapbook Playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLpGN3OSOxe87zUtiiwY3ifkYywgJobjPb

Stream Schedule:
Weekends - 4pm EST
Weekdays - TBD. I don't specifically schedule weekday streams. Check my twitter feed, join my discord channel, or join my steam group to see if I'm streaming! Weekday streams usually start at 4pm EST.
